@startuml Return State Machine
title Return Request State Machine Diagram
left to right direction

skinparam state {
    BackgroundColor#FFF3E0
    BorderColor#F57C00
    ArrowColor#424242
}

[*] --> SUBMITTED : Customer submits return request

SUBMITTED --> AWAITING_ITEMS : Request validated\n(reference order found)
SUBMITTED --> CANCELED : Customer cancels request

AWAITING_ITEMS --> IN_REVIEW : Warehouse receives items\n(staff marks received)
AWAITING_ITEMS --> CANCELED : Customer cancels\n(within allowed window)

IN_REVIEW --> APPROVED : Sales approves\n(item condition good)
IN_REVIEW --> REJECTED : Sales rejects\n(item damaged/not eligible)

APPROVED --> COMPLETED : Refund processed\n(VNPAY/Original payment)
APPROVED --> COMPLETED : Exchange order created

REJECTED --> [*] : Customer notified\n(items returned to customer)
COMPLETED --> [*] : Return completed
CANCELED --> [*] : Request cancelled

' ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
' NOTES
' ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

note right of SUBMITTED
  Return # generated
  Customer selects items
  Reason & photos provided
end note

note right of AWAITING_ITEMS
  Shipping label generated
  Customer notified of address
  7-day return window
end note

note right of IN_REVIEW
  Warehouse verifies items
  Sales inspect condition
  Photos documented
end note

note right of APPROVED
  Refund amount calculated
  Payment method determined
  Processing initiated
end note

note right of REJECTED
  Rejection reason provided
  Evidence photos shared
  Appeal option available
end note

@enduml
